&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join Wye Valley Community Stroke Services covering Herefordshire. This post is for a specialist Speech Therapist Band 6 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will be responsible for:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assessing and treating stroke patients within the community&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working with and supporting therapy support workers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assisting the team leader to further develop this new service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you are a Speech therapist who has experience of working with stroke and are keen to expand your skills then this is the role for you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will be a core member of the Community Stroke Service where we provide early supported discharge and ongoing therapy. We a very friendly team committed to providing high quality clinical care for patients and their carer’s &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
